==English==
From {{L.}} sui (of oneself) , from {{L.}} ''suus'' (one's own) , from [[Sanskrit]] ''sva'' (oneself) + [[-cide]]
===Noun===
'''suicide'''

# the killing of a person by his or her own hand
# a person who has killed him/herself

====Related terms====
*[[suicidal]]
*[[fratricide]]
